"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-travel-articles-1898555-event-tourism-olympics-culture-attractions-advice\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Theholidaybooking companyTravelLocalhas offered a number of tips that canhelp tourists avoid issueson an event holiday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Theholidaybooking companyTravelLocalhas\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 39}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 48, \"to\": 56}, {\"ngram\": \"tips\", \"from\": 60, \"to\": 64}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 78, \"to\": 86}, {\"ngram\": \"issueson\", \"from\": 93, \"to\": 101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spurred on by the upcoming Paris Olympics and the UEFA Euro 2024 in Germany, event holidays are a growing trend that see travellers visit a destination to witness an occasion.\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 150, \"end\": 164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 173, \"end\": 187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Euro_2024\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UEFA Euro 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Euro_2024\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Euro_2024\"}, {\"begin\": 191, \"end\": 198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.9469505040012594, \"rank\": 0.055633263909267476, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"event holidays\", \"from\": 200, \"to\": 214}, {\"ngram\": \"a growing trend\", \"from\": 219, \"to\": 234}, {\"ngram\": \"travellers\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 254}, {\"ngram\": \"a destination\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 274}, {\"ngram\": \"an occasion\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Huw Owen, co-founder of TravelLocal, noted that destinations hosting events will besignificantly more crowdedthan at other times of the year.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 309, \"end\": 317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huw_Owen\", \"score\": 0.999999999806505, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Huw Owen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huw_Owen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huw_Owen\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"co\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"founder\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 329}, {\"ngram\": \"TravelLocal\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"destinations\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"hosting events\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 384}, {\"ngram\": \"other times\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He explained: \\\"Large events are always going to stir excitement and pull in the crowds and usually these events take place inmajor cities.\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Large events\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowds\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 538}, {\"ngram\": \"these events\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 574}, {\"ngram\": \"inmajor cities\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would always advise against travelling during peak season or visiting tourist hotspots during busy periods - however it would be naive to assume that people are not going to travel to experience their favourite event.\\\"\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"peak season\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 652}, {\"ngram\": \"tourist hotspots\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"busy periods\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"their favourite event\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Traveller shares flying tip that helps tourists if they lose their bag To help get the best experience from an event holiday, TravelLocal has urged tourists to never let the occasion itself get in the way of the local culture.\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Traveller shares\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"flying tip\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 872}, {\"ngram\": \"their bag\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"the best experience\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 927}, {\"ngram\": \"an event holiday\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"TravelLocal\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"the occasion\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"the local culture\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before setting off, the company recommended taking the time to research the destination for other nearby attractions in which they could learn about the history of the area and the typical way of life.\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"the destination\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1143}, {\"ngram\": \"other nearby attractions\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"the typical way\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They can also respect local residents by looking after the destination's environment by disposing of waste responsibly and, where possible, utilising reusable items.\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"local residents\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"the destination's environment\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"waste\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"reusable items\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:European city with incredibly walkable streets offers culture and amazing food Do not miss:Holiday destination with cheapest tourist tax named Do not miss:'Safe and happy' country is one of the best for Brits to retire to We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"European city\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"incredibly walkable streets\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1484}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"amazing food\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"Holiday destination\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"cheapest tourist tax\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"Do not miss:'Safe and happy' country\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"Brits\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"your sign-up\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1679}, {\"ngram\": \"content\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1706}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adverts\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1799}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1807}, {\"ngram\": \"3rd parties\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1823}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy Huw also recommended that tourists should try to avoid international brands in favour of local shops and cafes, which can help them find unique souvenirs whilst supporting independent businesses.\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy Huw\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"international brands\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1983}, {\"ngram\": \"favour\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"local shops\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"cafes\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2018}, {\"ngram\": \"unique souvenirs\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2061}, {\"ngram\": \"independent businesses\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He advised: \\\"Supporting local communities can come in many forms; from purchasing souvenirs from local markets and independent shops, to dining at locally owned restaurants, bars and cafes.\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"local communities\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"many forms\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"souvenirs\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2197}, {\"ngram\": \"local markets\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2216}, {\"ngram\": \"independent shops\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"locally owned restaurants\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"bars\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2284}, {\"ngram\": \"cafes\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no better way to appreciate a destination's true culture, and I would always encourage travellers to choose local businesses over international chains.\\\"\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no better way\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2320}, {\"ngram\": \"a destination's true culture\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"travellers\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2404}, {\"ngram\": \"local businesses\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2431}, {\"ngram\": \"international chains\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally, Huw suggested that tourists who want to leave the least impact on the environment should consider staying at an eco-friendly form of accommodation.\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2617, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Huw\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"the least impact\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2532}, {\"ngram\": \"the environment\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2551}, {\"ngram\": \"an eco-friendly form\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"accommodation\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"There are accommodations that prioritise sustainable initiatives, such as eco-lodges, green hotels or resorts with eco-certifications.\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"accommodations\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2654}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainable initiatives\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"eco-lodges\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"green hotels\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2728}, {\"ngram\": \"resorts\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2739}, {\"ngram\": \"eco-certifications\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Many of these establishments utilise renewable energy sources, implement water conservation measures and support local communities through responsible tourism practices.\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these establishments\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"renewable energy sources\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2828}, {\"ngram\": \"water conservation measures\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2867}, {\"ngram\": \"local communities\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2897}, {\"ngram\": \"responsible tourism practices\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also provide an experience that you often can not find anywhere else.\\\"\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 3012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an experience\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH CONNECT WITH US TODAY'S PAPER See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3151, \"end\": 3164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2301713996912673e-17, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SEARCH CONNECT\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3028}, {\"ngram\": \"US TODAY'S PAPER\", \"from\": 3034, \"to\": 3050}, {\"ngram\": \"today's front and back pages\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3083}, {\"ngram\": \"the newspaper\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3114}, {\"ngram\": \"issues\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3200, \"end\": 3213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2301713996912673e-17, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}], \"noun_ph